external_knowledge:
- "treasured creations" refers to posts with the most likes (no_of_likes);
- "popular artists" refers to users who have at least 10 followers;
- "garnered a large entourage of at least 10 admirers" refers to users with at least 10 followers (COUNT(followed_user_id) >= 10).

sql:
SELECT post_id, no_of_likes
FROM posts
WHERE no_of_likes = (SELECT MAX(no_of_likes) FROM posts);

SELECT username, created_at 
FROM users 
WHERE user_id = '1';

